E_D("replace into `imicms_img` values('296','15','695546574','夏季】怎样补水保湿 让皮肤水当当方法？','','夏季特殊的天气变化，肌肤容易出现过敏、季节性缺水等现象，快来学习下春季怎样补水保湿。','34','美容','https://mp.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/getimgdata?mode=large&source=file&fileId=208596497&token=1860','1','<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">1、洁肤去角质</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	皮肤干燥，护肤品难吸收，肌肤表层堆积的厚厚角质层单靠洗面奶是很难清理干净的，这是需要使用温顺的<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/qujuezhi/\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/qujuezhi/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">去角质</a>凝露、磨砂膏等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong>建议：</strong>每两周去一次角质，不要清洁过度。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">2、锁水保湿</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	给肌肤喝饱水才能更好地锁住水分，在晚上睡觉前敷个<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">保湿</a><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/mianmo/\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/mianmo/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">面膜</a>可以远离干燥起皮，让肌肤焕然一新。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong>注意：</strong>由于夏季天气特殊，除了有干燥起皮的问题，还容易出现皮肤过敏的现象，尽量选择温顺、低敏感的补水护肤品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">3、眼唇手的保湿</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	除了脸部<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">保湿</a>，嘴唇、眼睛、双手的护理也不能少，晚上<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/xilian/\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/xilian/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">洗脸</a>的时候，拿热毛巾敷敷嘴唇，用热水泡泡手，擦完<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/zhengxing/changshi/\" target=\"_blank\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/zhengxing/changshi/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">美容</a>水，给眼睛涂个合适的<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/TaoBao/HuFu/49632.shtml\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/TaoBao/HuFu/49632.shtml\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">眼霜</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong>注意：</strong>嘴唇上起干皮的时候一定不能直接撕掉，应用热毛巾轻轻捂在嘴唇上，然后用棉签将软化后的死皮轻轻擦掉，涂上滋润的甘油即可\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">4、保湿喷雾</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	经常坐在办公室的OL，环境干燥，在办公桌上常备一款<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">保湿</a><a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/penwu\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/penwu\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">喷雾</a>，有效恢复肌肤水润感，赶走干燥，除了可以给肌肤随时随地补水滋润，还能调节肌肤水油平衡。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\">5、画圈圈保湿</span></strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"clear:both;white-space:normal;text-indent:2em;color:#666666;font-family:Simsun;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;\">\r\n	“画圈圈”式的肌肤<span id=\"0_nwp\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;float:none;\"><a id=\"0_nwl\" href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%B0%B4%C4%A6&amp;k0=%B0%B4%C4%A6&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=4&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" target=\"_blank\" mpid=\"0\" _href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%B0%B4%C4%A6&amp;k0=%B0%B4%C4%A6&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=4&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;width:auto;height:auto;\">按摩</span></a></span>能够促进保养品的<span id=\"1_nwp\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;float:none;\"><a id=\"1_nwl\" href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%CE%FC%CA%D5&amp;k0=%CE%FC%CA%D5&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=2&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" target=\"_blank\" mpid=\"1\" _href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%CE%FC%CA%D5&amp;k0=%CE%FC%CA%D5&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=2&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;width:auto;height:auto;\">吸收</span></a></span>，更能促进肌肤的<span id=\"2_nwp\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;float:none;\"><a id=\"2_nwl\" href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%D0%C2%B3%C2%B4%FA%D0%BB&amp;k0=%D0%C2%B3%C2%B4%FA%D0%BB&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=3&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" target=\"_blank\" mpid=\"2\" _href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%D0%C2%B3%C2%B4%FA%D0%BB&amp;k0=%D0%C2%B3%C2%B4%FA%D0%BB&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=3&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;width:auto;height:auto;\">新陈代谢</span></a></span>，首先用双手的四根手指的指腹，在下巴处轻轻地画圈圈，接着是<span id=\"3_nwp\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;float:none;\"><a id=\"3_nwl\" href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%C1%B3%BC%D5&amp;k0=%C1%B3%BC%D5&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=5&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" target=\"_blank\" mpid=\"3\" _href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%C1%B3%BC%D5&amp;k0=%C1%B3%BC%D5&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=5&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;width:auto;height:auto;\">脸颊</span></a></span>，从内向外温柔地画三大圈圈，然后是眼周，从内到外画三次大圈圈，从脸部中央向外，从<span id=\"4_nwp\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;float:none;\"><a id=\"4_nwl\" href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%B6%EE%CD%B7&amp;k0=%B6%EE%CD%B7&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=1&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" target=\"_blank\" mpid=\"4\" _href=\"http://cpro.baidu.com/cpro/ui/uijs.php?adclass=0&amp;app_id=0&amp;c=news&amp;cf=1001&amp;ch=0&amp;di=128&amp;fv=17&amp;is_app=0&amp;jk=9bb06d1f89129550&amp;k=%B6%EE%CD%B7&amp;k0=%B6%EE%CD%B7&amp;kdi0=0&amp;luki=1&amp;n=10&amp;p=baidu&amp;q=95020170_cpr&amp;rb=0&amp;rs=1&amp;seller_id=1&amp;sid=509512891f6db09b&amp;ssp2=1&amp;stid=0&amp;t=tpclicked3_hc&amp;tu=u1830978&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2E2liang%2Enet%2Fbaoyang%2F201503%2F121078%2Eshtml&amp;urlid=0\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\"><span style=\"color:#0000FF;width:auto;height:auto;\">额头</span></a></span>、眼睛下方、下巴到脸颊，轻轻地触摸，让脸部肌肤稍做休息后结束. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;想要细嫩润滑的肌肤，以上这些<a class=\"channel_keylink\" href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" _href=\"http://www.2liang.net/baoyang/bsbs/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#666666;\">保湿</a>补水的方法可以告别夏季干燥肌，让肌肤水嫩，还等什么？赶紧行动哦。\r\n</p>','','1436542384','1436542384','2','2a94af5381fcc932','夏季】怎样补水保湿 让皮肤水当当方法？','','295','0','','','','1','1','0','1','','');");
E_D("replace into `imicms_img` values('297','15','695546574','【有着一颗减肥的心和一个能吃的胃】','','无论是明星还是普通人，减肥前后对比照片都很惊艳，这就是减肥带来的效果，赶快行动起来吧！','33','美体','https://mp.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/getimgdata?mode=large&source=file&fileId=208597108&token=186015582&lang=zh_CN','1','左边叫投资，右边叫省钱；左边叫精致，右边叫没时间；左边叫爱自己，右边叫嫌麻烦；喜欢左边年轻态还是右边衰老态? &nbsp;好好爱自己。很喜欢这句话：你若高贵，一切都便宜，你若便宜，一切都很贵。什么都没有你自己贵！送给舍得为自己投资的人们。该买就买该花就花！好好爱自己，狠狠爱自己！........<br />\r\n<div style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>','','1436543365','1436543365','2','2a94af5381fcc932','【有着一颗减肥的心和一个能吃的胃】','','296','0','','','','1','1','0','1','','');");
